Dialogue: 5,0:01:54.31,0:02:00.89,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{In order for Luffy and Robin to get some rest,\Nthe Going Merry anchored off the uninhabited island for four days. - OG}{\q2}Luffy e Robin precisavam se recuperar, então o {\i1}Going Merry{\i0}\Npermaneceu ancorado na ilha desabitada por quatro dias.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.89,0:02:05.85,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{After that, we sailed out. This is the third morning since we started our voyage again. - OG}{\q2}Depois disso, zarpamos, e agora este é\No terceiro dia desde que retomamos a viagem.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.69,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's a fine day today, partly spring... - OG}O tempo hoje é uma bela mistura de primavera...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.61,0:02:11.31,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{[/i1]peppered with occasional bouts of summer. - OG}{\i1}e alguns momentos de verão.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que lindo dia!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.09,0:02:22.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Nami-[/i1]swan[/i0]!}Nami, minha doce!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.60,0:02:30.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I made [/i1]pomme paille[/i0].\NMademoiselle, if you like... - OG}Eu fiz {\i1}pomme paille{\i0}.\NMademoiselle, se quiser...{Z}
Comment: 5,0:02:25.60,0:02:30.29,Note-207+,,0,0,0,,pomme paille: shoe string potatoes
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hmm, this is good! - OG}Mmm, está delicioso!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.10,0:02:36.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm so happy! - OG}Estou radiante!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up, you jerk.\NYou're disturbing my sleep! - OG}Fica quieto! Eu tô tentando dormir!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.47,0:02:43.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, é... Desculpa, cabeça de cacto.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What'd you say, you dartboard jerk?! - OG}O que você disse, sobrancelha de alvo?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dar– What'd you\Njust say, you bastard?! - OG}Al– Eu ouvi direito, seu desgraçado?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.95,0:02:50.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dartboard eyebrows. - OG}Sobrancelha de alvo.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.64,0:02:57.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Yeah! Luffy! Isso aí!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.61,0:03:02.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Yeah! Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.43,0:03:06.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{At last! - OG}Finalmente!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.64,0:03:06.98,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm impersonating my frozen self. - OG}Essa é minha imitação de quando eu congelei.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.72,0:03:27.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que isso...? Eu não acredito que ele tá fazendo isso\Ndepois de ter congelado e quase morrido.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Did I do a good job? - OG}Ficou parecido?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You did! You looked exactly like that, Luffy! - OG}Ficou perfeito! Era igualzinho, Luffy!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Limpa isso direitinho, tá, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.87,0:03:38.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm...? Ah! O que você tá comendo, Nami?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É {\i1}paille{\i0}, um prato de batata.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.94,0:03:45.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Batata, é? Eu também tô com fome. Ei, Sanji!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Just how much sleep\Ndo you need to be satisfied?! - OG}Quanto de sono você precisa, afinal?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.96,0:03:52.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How much sleep I "need" is my business!\NI'll take you on if you wanna fight! - OG}Quanto de sono eu "preciso" é\Nda {\i1}minha{\i0} conta! Vamos resolver isso!{Z - CPS}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.59,0:04:06.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They said this is called paille. Yummy! - OG}Disseram que isso se chama {\i1}paille{\i0}. É bom!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O que é {\i1}paille{\i0}?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.58,0:04:12.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's the tail meat of a huge monster Paille. - OG}É a carne da cauda de um monstro\Nenorme chamado Paille.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.65,0:04:16.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I killed it. It was at least 100 meters high. - OG}Eu matei ele. Tinha pelo menos\Ncem metros de altura.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{100 meters?!\NThat's amazing, Usopp! - OG}Cem metros?! Isso é incrível, Usopp!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hmm, a piece of cake.\NI did it before breakfast. - OG}É, e fiz tudo isso antes do café da manhã.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? Você acordou cedo e matou ele?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper, fala meu nome.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.49,0:04:31.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê? É, claro, C-Capitão...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.08,0:04:35.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo! Meu nome é Capitão... Usopp–
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yoo-hoo! Robin-chwan! - OG}Ei! Robin meu amor!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How are you feeling?\NDo you feel a chill? - OG}Como você tá se sentindo? Tá com frio?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.51,0:04:50.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm feeling a lot better.\NThank you, my excellent doctor! - OG}Estou me sentindo muito melhor\Ngraças a um médico incrível.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.97,0:04:56.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh... Being called an excellent doctor wouldn't make me feel happy or anything, you jerk. - OG}Ah, ser chamado de médico incrível não\Nme deixa feliz nem nada, sua idiota.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ele parece bem feliz.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.44,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vai com calma, Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.27,0:05:05.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You might feel uneasy when you see Luffy being as good as new after having the same experience as you, - OG}Não se pressione só porque o Luffy já tá\Nde pé depois de passar pela mesma coisa.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but you can take your time\Nand rest, you know. - OG}Tudo bem ir com calma e descansar.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Yay! \N– Isso não foi um elogio!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.73,0:05:13.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Robin-chan! Shall I make\Nsomething that can warm you up? - OG}Robin! Quer que eu faça algo\Npra te aquecer?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.23,0:05:14.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do you have an appetite? - OG}Como tá o apetite?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.38,0:05:16.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then... - OG}Bom...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,posso tomar um café?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.30,0:05:21.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay! It's my pleasure! - OG}Claro! Será um prazer!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.69,0:05:36.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What the hell is that? - OG}O que é aquilo?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.07,0:05:50.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Anyway, this paille thing is so good that we can't stop eating, isn't it? - OG}Enfim, esse negócio de {\i1}paille{\i0} é tão bom\Nque a gente não para de comer.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,É, é delicioso!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, if we sell this thing,\Ndon't you think we can make some money? - OG}{Hey, d'ya think we'd make a killing selling this stuff? - Z}Quanto a gente ganharia se vendesse isso?{Gaijin}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,U-u-um sapo tá nadando de crawl!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It went to your side,\Nso take a look at it! - OG}Ele foi pro seu lado, dá uma olhada!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Isso é verdade?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A frog...? Could it be that frog? - OG}Um sapo...? Será aquele sapo?{OG}{A frog? Like, a real frog? - Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.38,0:06:09.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Luffy, are you taking what\Nthat stupid admiral said seriously? - OG}Ei, Luffy, você tá levando a sério o que\Naquele almirante idiota disse?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To start with, there's no way\Na frog would do the front cra...}Pra começo de conversa, um sapo nunca faria o–
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.55,0:06:14.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, it is! A-A frog is doing the front crawl! - OG}Tá fazendo mesmo! U-Um sapo tá nadando de crawl!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll follow it, guys! - OG}Vamos seguir ele, galera!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.15,0:06:16.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! - OG}– Sim!\N– Sim!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Recolham a vela! Preparem os remos!\NVirem o navio pra duas horas!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.80,0:06:21.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{– Yeah!\N– Yeah! - OG}– Sim!\N– Sim!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.86,0:06:22.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hurry up}Mais rápido!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.89,0:06:26.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know why, but I feel\Nlike we have to go after it! - OG}Não sei explicar, mas eu não consigo\Nresistir a vontade de ir atrás dele!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Desculpa a demora, mademoiselles.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que isso...?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O quê?! O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Seems like the ship changed course. - OG}Parece que o navio mudou de curso.{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.96,0:06:44.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Hey, you guys! Why'd you change\Nthe course without asking me?! - OG}Ei, vocês! Quem disse que podiam\Nmudar de curso sem me consultar?!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, Nami, escuta isso!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A gente achou um sapo enorme\Ncom cicatrizes por todo o corpo!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Que isso?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.68,0:06:55.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're definitely gonna roast it whole and eat it! - OG}O plano é assar ele inteiro e comer!{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Vocês vão comer?!\N– Vocês vão comer?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ei, é verdade.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hm? Isso é um farol?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.60,0:07:08.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why is there a lighthouse in a place like that?\NI wonder if someone's there... - OG}Por que tem um farol tão longe\Nassim? Será que tem alguém lá...{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What's the matter? Do you see an island? - OG}O-O que você vê? É uma ilha?{Z}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.53,0:07:14.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, there's a lighthouse. A log pose wouldn't point to that sort of place. - OG}Não, é um farol. Log poses\Nnão deveriam apontar pra esse tipo de lugar.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What about the frog? Tell us\Nthe direction the frog went! - OG}E o sapo? Fala pra gente\Na direção que o sapo foi!{Z}
